Purpose
-------
Reusable institutional trade statistics.

Provides

• Win Rate
• Loss Rate
• Average Win
• Average Loss
• Profit Factor
• Expectancy
• Average Holding Period
• Turnover

Used By

• Performance Engine
• Reporting
• Dashboard
